metadata.name: The green room
metadata.description:
Hope is everywhere. Healing is everywhere. Growth is everywhere. Harmony is everywhere. You are everywhere.

Digital artwork created with the color #003E39 and with the photograph of a person in an anonymous everyday situation.

Comes with a signed 1/1 print of the work. 
Giclée printing, Hahnemühle Photo Rag, 18" x 25"
